trans-unit.source: Adds an <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> to the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 添加到 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" /> 中。

trans-unit.source: The index at which the item has been added.
trans-unit.target: 已添加了项的索引。

trans-unit.source: If `Count` already equals the capacity, the capacity of list is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array and copying the existing elements to the new array before the new element is added.
trans-unit.target: 如果`Count`已等于容量、 通过自动重新分配在内部数组并将现有的元素复制到新数组，然后才能添加新元素的列表容量加倍。

trans-unit.source: If `Count` is less than the capacity, this method is an 0(1) operation.
trans-unit.target: 如果`Count`小于容量，此方法为 0 （1） 运算。

trans-unit.source: If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, this method becomes an 0(n) operation, where n is `Count`.
trans-unit.target: 如果容量需要增加以容纳新元素，此方法将成为 0 （n） 操作，其中 n 是`Count`。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> method expects only <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> and its derived types (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) as parameters.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A>方法应只<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal>及其派生类型 (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>， <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>，和<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) 作为参数。

trans-unit.source: Indicates if the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> is in the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 指示指定的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 是否在 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" /> 中。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified qualified name is in the collection; otherwise, returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定限定名在集合内，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If null is supplied, <see langword="false" /> is returned because there is no qualified name with a null name.
trans-unit.target: 如果提供了空值，会因为没有具有空名称的限定名而返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 一维数组，它是从 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" /> 中复制的元素的目标。

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: 该数组的索引必须从零开始。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in the array at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: 数组中开始复制的位置的索引（从零开始）。

trans-unit.source: Copies all the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" />s from the collection into the given array, starting at the given index.
trans-unit.target: 将集合中的所有 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 复制到给定数组中并从给定索引处开始。

trans-unit.source: The specified array must be of a compatible type.
trans-unit.target: 指定的数组必须具有兼容类型。

trans-unit.source: This method uses <xref:System.Array.Copy%2A> to copy the elements.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使用<xref:System.Array.Copy%2A>要复制的元素。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 为空引用（在 Visual Basic 中为 <see langword="Nothing" />）。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 小于零。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is multi-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> 是多维的。

trans-unit.source: \- or -
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the length of <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> 等于或大于 <paramref name="array" /> 的长度。

trans-unit.source: \- or -
The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> is greater than the available space from index to the end of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 源 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 中的元素数大于从索引到目标数组末尾处的可用空间。

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: 源 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 的类型无法自动转换为目标数组的类型。

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator for iterating through the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjects" /> contained in the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 返回用于循环访问 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjects" /> 中包含的 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" /> 的枚举数。

trans-unit.source: The iterator returns <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectEnumerator" />.
trans-unit.target: 该迭代程序返回 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectEnumerator" />。

trans-unit.target: 获取与指定的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 相对应的集合索引。

trans-unit.source: The index corresponding to the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" />.
trans-unit.target: 与指定的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 相对应的索引。

trans-unit.source: Inserts an <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> to the <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" /> 插入 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" />。

trans-unit.source: If `Count` already equals the capacity, the capacity of the list is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果`Count`已经等于容量、 列表的容量翻倍通过自动重新分配在内部数组，才能插入新元素。

trans-unit.source: If `index` is equal to `Count`, `value` is added to the end of `XmlSchemaObjectCollection`.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`等同于`Count`，`value`添加到末尾`XmlSchemaObjectCollection`。

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 在插入点之后的元素将下移以容纳新元素。

trans-unit.target: 从 <see langword="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" /> 移除 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject" />。

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法执行的线性搜索;因此，平均执行时间成正比<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: That is, this method is an O(`n`) operation, where `n` is <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 也就是说，此方法为 O (`n`) 操作，其中`n`是<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: This method determines equality by calling <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 此方法通过调用可确定相等性<xref:System.Object.Equals%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed element move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 移除的元素下面的元素将上移以占用空出的位置。
